text: Toto is the surname of: * Anthony Toto (1498–1554), Italian painter and architect * Gerald Toto (born 1967), French composer and performer * Jonathan Toto (born 1990), French footballer of Cameroonian heritage * Ismet Toto (1908–1937), Albanian bureaucrat, publicist, writer and political activist * Paolo Totò (born 1991), Italian cyclist ==See also== *Tono (name)
title: Toto (surname)
